  "message": "feat(writing): add OpenGraph image for CMA-ES optimization article\n\nCreate dynamic social preview image for the CMA-ES explainer article\nusing Next.js edge-runtime ImageResponse API.\n\nVisual Design:\n- Dark gradient background (#0a0a12 to #121620) consistent with site\n- Amber/orange/red color scheme matching the article's theme\n- Subtle grid pattern overlay for texture\n- Dual glowing orbs: amber top-left, red bottom-right for depth\n\nLeft Panel - CMA-ES Visualization:\n- Abstract SVG ellipsoid representing covariance matrix adaptation\n- Rotated ellipses at -35\u00b0 to show search distribution shape\n- Gradient stroke (amber \u2192 orange \u2192 red) for visual interest\n- Sample points around centroid showing population sampling\n- Dashed trajectory line indicating optimization path\n- Outer glow effect via blurred radial gradient\n\nRight Panel - Content:\n- Category pill: \"Intelligence / Adaptive Search\"\n- Two-line title with gradient text:\n  - \"The Incredible Magic of\" in white gradient\n  - \"CMA-ES\" in amber/orange/red gradient\n- Descriptive subtitle in muted slate\n- Three feature tags: Black-Box Opt, Geometry, No Gradients\n- Each tag has matching color scheme with subtle backgrounds\n\nLayout:\n- 1200\u00d7630px standard OG dimensions\n- Bottom gradient accent bar in amber \u2192 red\n- Domain watermark in top-right corner\n- Centered flex layout with 60px gap between panels\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
